    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving atmospheric engineering, powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a professional subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS bulletproofing, ensuring the chassis and valvetrain remain resilient under load. The ZF 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, precise gates, while the factory limited-slip differential ensures optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. The suspension geometry is perfectly dialed, with all bushings and dampers functioning at peak performance. Finished in a deep Carbon Black with impeccable paint depth and zero panel gap variance, this vehicle represents a true collector-grade investment for the discerning driver who demands mechanical transparency and visceral performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
