      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been exclusively garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a deep, glass-like paint finish completely free of swirls, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of preservation; the premium leather seats remain firm and uncreased, the carpets are pristine, and it retains that unmistakable new-car aroma. Every electronic feature, from the navigation system to the ambient lighting, functions with factory-spec precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented, full-service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. The engine bay is immaculate, reflecting the same level of care as the exterior. For the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this is a rare opportunity to own a showroom-standard specimen. Includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a folder of every service record from day one.",
